Coinbase announced it has hired Tina Bhatnagar as vice president of operations and technology. Bhatnagar will head up customer service teams for the Coinbase and GDAX exchanges, and will work to improve customer experience. She will ensure that Coinbase meets its commitment to double the size of its support team over the next three months and expand 24/7 phone support to all customers by the end of June. Bhatnagar was previously vice president of operations and user services at Twitter.